      "Application Notes": "The MPU-6050 is a 6-DoF accelerometer and gyroscope. It uses I2C communication. The breakout board includes a voltage regulator to accept 3-5V input and provides a 3.3V output. The I2C address can be changed by pulling AD0 high. The INT pin can be configured for interrupt output. The sensor has a temperature sensor and can measure acceleration and angular velocity. The breakout board has STEMMA QT connectors for easy connection."
